<h1>Standings
<% if @season.id %>
for <%= @season.name %>
<% end %>
</h1>

<%= render :partial => 'common/season_select' %>

<h3>Season</h3>

<table class="bordered">
<tr>
  <th>Team</th>
  <th>Place</th>
  <th>Points</th>
  <th>Goal diff</th>
  <th>Goals for</th>
  <th>Goals against</th>
  <th>Wins</th>
  <th>Ties</th>
  <th>Losses</th>
  <% if @logged_in %>
  <th>Head to head</th>
  <% end %>
</tr>
<% @season_standings.each do |standing| %>
<tr>
  <td><%= standing.team.display %></td>
  <td align="right"><%= standing.rank %></td>
  <td align="right"><%= standing.points %></td>
  <td align="right"><%= standing.goal_diff %></td>
  <td align="right"><%= standing.goals_for %></td>
  <td align="right"><%= standing.goals_against %></td>
  <td align="right"><%= standing.wins %></td>
  <td align="right"><%= standing.ties %></td>
  <td align="right"><%= standing.losses %></td>
  <% if @logged_in %>
  <td align="right"><%= standing.hth_wins %><%= standing.hth_ties %><%= standing.hth_losses %></td>
  <% end %>
</tr>
<% end %>
</table>
<p>Regular Season Rankings are calculated in order of most points to least points with the following tie-breakers, in order:</p>

<ol>
  <li>points</li>

  <li>win tie loss record between the tied teams</li>

  <li>goal differential (goals for minus goals against) (over the whole season)</li>

  <li>goals for (over the whole season)</li>

  <li>least goals against (over the whole season)</li>

  <li>most wins</li>

  <li>most ties</li>

  <li>least losses</li>
</ol>

<p>Constitution 2.6.2 - Tie Breaking for first place at the end of the regular season -  If 2 or more teams are still tied for first place at the end of the league season, placement shall be decided by the win, loss, tie record between the tied teams. If this fails to break the tie, goal difference in games between the tied teams shall be used.  If there is still no outright result, goals for in games between the tied teams during the entire league schedule shall be used. If still necessary,  placement will be decided by a penalty shoot-out involving the tied teams.

<h3>Playoffs</h3>

<table class="bordered">
<tr>
  <th>Team</th>
  <th>Pool</th>
  <th>Place</th>
  <th>Points</th>
  <th>Goal diff <sup>1</sup></th>
  <th>Goals for <sup>2</sup></th>
  <th>Goals against</th>
